## 1. EF Core 6 — Query Rules

**KHÔNG BAO GIỜ:**
```csharp
// ❌ Full table scan
await _db.Orders.ToListAsync(ct);

// ❌ N+1
foreach (var o in orders)
    o.Items = await _db.OrderItems.Where(i => i.OrderId == o.Id).ToListAsync();

// ❌ Load entity chỉ để update 1 field
var m = await _db.MenuItems.FindAsync(id);
m.Price = newPrice;
await _db.SaveChangesAsync();
```

**LUÔN DÙNG:**
```csharp
// ✅ Project → DTO tại DB
var dto = await _db.Orders.AsNoTracking()
    .Where(o => o.Id == id)
    .Select(o => new OrderDto {
        Id = o.Id, Status = o.Status,
        Total = o.Items.Sum(i => i.Qty * i.Price)
    }).FirstOrDefaultAsync(ct);

// ✅ Pagination bắt buộc
var page = await _db.Orders.AsNoTracking()
    .Where(o => o.StoreId == storeId)
    .OrderByDescending(o => o.CreatedAt)
    .Skip(req.Page * req.PageSize).Take(req.PageSize)
    .Select(o => new OrderSummaryDto { ... }).ToListAsync(ct);

// ✅ Batch load (diệt N+1)
var items = await _db.OrderItems.AsNoTracking()
    .Where(i => orderIds.Contains(i.OrderId)).ToListAsync(ct);
var byOrder = items.ToLookup(i => i.OrderId);

// ✅ Update không load entity
var entry = new MenuItem { Id = id, Price = newPrice };
_db.MenuItems.Attach(entry);
_db.Entry(entry).Property(x => x.Price).IsModified = true;
await _db.SaveChangesAsync(ct);

// ✅ Count tại DB
var count = await _db.Orders.Where(o => o.StoreId == sid).CountAsync(ct);
```

