## 6. .NET 6 / C# 10 — Bảng giới hạn

| ❌ KHÔNG dùng | Chỉ có từ | ✅ Thay thế .NET 6 |
|---|---|---|
| Primary constructors `class S(IRepo r)` | C# 12 | Standard constructor |
| Collection expressions `[1, 2, 3]` | C# 12 | `new List<int> { 1, 2, 3 }` |
| `FrozenDictionary<K,V>` | .NET 8 | `IReadOnlyDictionary<K,V>` |
| `SearchValues<T>` | .NET 8 | `HashSet<T>` |
| `TimeProvider` | .NET 8 | `DateTimeOffset.UtcNow` |
| `IExceptionHandler` | .NET 8 | Custom middleware |
| `AddResilienceHandler` | Polly v8 / .NET 7 | `AddPolicyHandler` (Polly v7) |
| `[GeneratedRegex]` | .NET 7 | `new Regex(p, RegexOptions.Compiled)` |
| `ArgumentException.ThrowIfNullOrEmpty` | .NET 7 | Manual null/empty check |

**✅ OK trong .NET 6:** `record` · `init` · `IAsyncEnumerable<T>` · `Span<T>` · `ArrayPool<T>` · `ValueTask<T>` · `Random.Shared` · `ArgumentNullException.ThrowIfNull` · `CreateAsyncScope()` · `EF.CompileAsyncQuery` · `IOptionsMonitor<T>` · `DbContextPool`

