## 7. Observability

```csharp
// ✅ Structured logging — KHÔNG string interpolation
_logger.LogInformation(
    "Order {OrderId} created for Store {StoreId}. Total: {Total:C}",
    order.Id, order.StoreId, order.Total);

// ❌ Interpolation + ❌ Log PII
_logger.LogInformation($"Order {order.Id}");         // BAD — no structure
_logger.LogDebug("Token: {Token}", jwtToken);         // BAD — PII

// ✅ LogError phải pass exception object — không chỉ .Message
_logger.LogError(ex, "Order {OrderId} failed", orderId);  // ✅
_logger.LogError($"Error: {ex.Message}");                 // ❌ mất stack trace

// ✅ OpenTelemetry span
using var activity = AppTelemetry.Source.StartActivity("Order.Create");
activity?.SetTag("store.id", cmd.StoreId.ToString());
activity?.SetTag("order.item_count", cmd.Items.Count);
```
